  "detailed_description": "Caterva is a top-down rougelike shooter where you control a multitude of clone slaves.<br>And you have to lead the way to the exit.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/ee4468b71a10a19ec304df4af88f1328.poster.avif?t=1678534020\" width=526 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/ee4468b71a10a19ec304df4af88f1328.webm?t=1678534020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/ee4468b71a10a19ec304df4af88f1328.mp4?t=1678534020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The more slaves you save, the more powerful and vulnerable you will become.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/318759f9afb4405aa68a458733e1766c.poster.avif?t=1678534020\" width=526 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/318759f9afb4405aa68a458733e1766c.webm?t=1678534020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>All the clones have their own weapon and fire them at one, so when you get a lot of slaves you become incredibly deadly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/c3a11b3a8a80ecd56b682431e7ba5ccd.poster.avif?t=1678534020\" width=524 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/c3a11b3a8a80ecd56b682431e7ba5ccd.webm?t=1678534020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1352450/extras/c3a11b3a8a80ecd56b682431e7ba5ccd.mp4?t=1678534020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
